    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Scroll of Bane</strong> (Level 1 Enchantment)</p><p>Up to three creatures of your choice that you can see within range must make charisma saving throws. Whenever a target that fails this saving throw makes an attack roll or a saving throw before the spell ends, the target must roll a d4 and subtract the number rolled from the attack roll or saving throw.</p><p><em>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, you can target one additional creature for each slot level above 1st.</em></p><p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S, M (A drop of blood.)</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action | <strong>Range:</strong> 30 feet | <strong>Duration:</strong> Up to 1 minute (Concentration)</p><p><em>Classes: Bard, Cleric</em></p>",
